{
  "stem": "5496.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we had to-- I had a shovel that I could hardly lift.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were, allegedly, doing this work from morning until night, outdoors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were back to the barracks, and we stayed there until about, almost January or end of December of 1944.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], you think it was--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We keep thinking, because it couldn't be too far from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only it was a very short train ride, and I cannot find it on the map.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was definitely a slave labor camp for women only.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as I said, there were the anti-tank ditches.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By then, of course, rumors were-- and even we heard it-- that the Russians are approaching.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So one day, they herded us into a row.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's when the infamous death march to Bergen-Belsen started.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- yes, we were-- we were aware.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we also heard-- I mean, there were some prisoners that came around doing some odd duties.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know who they were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were political prisoner, men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were telling us that it's [GERMAN], which means, of course, that it's a camp where we are for one purpose only.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that sooner or later, you see that smoke, they would point out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's where you're going to wind up yourself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they are the ones who told us that the children were thrown alive into these pits.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And older people were taken to the-- what they called, euphemistically, a shower, which was, of course, the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we found out from them, otherwise we wouldn't have known.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We-- and the smell, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then we realized the dreadful smell, and we knew those were the burned bodies that we smelled.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we did-- we had no knowledge where.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
